name: All Nippon Airways 787-8 Very Foggy Takeoff From Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Yet another foggy day video from Paine Field... Here we have an All Nippon Airways Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner departing Paine Field in Everett, Washington on a routine test flight, in very foggy weather. Fellow spotter CphSpotting caught the exact same aircraft standing right beside me - Check out his video here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q2zjOxauLoI

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
